# Paper evidence snapshots are small, curated JSON artifacts even though they
# live under a path segment named "data".
!paper/exp/data/
!paper/exp/data/**
paper/exp/data/run_snapshots/**/intermediate/
paper/exp/data/run_snapshots/**/predictions/
paper/exp/data/run_snapshots/**/checkpoints/
